description=CleanUI replaces the default inventory, loot, and context UI with a cleaner and more compact layout. <LINE> This is the Build 42.15.x version. <LINE> Includes a defensive patch for invalid repair/fixing definitions in the inventory context menu. <LINE> There are also variants for builds 42.16+, 42.13-42.14 and legacy 42.12.x. <LINE> Adds a guard for right-click context menus on stale or virtual containers in MP.